23 PM / in 11 minutes BRIEF-Global Green Solutions Signs MoU With Kaset Thai International Sugar Corp​ Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Global Green Solutions Inc: 
* CO ‍SIGNED MOU TO INVEST IN BIOCOMPLEX IN NAKHON SAWAN PROVINCE WITH KASET THAI INTERNATIONAL SUGAR CORP​ 
* INVESTMENT VALUE OF FIRST PHASE EXPECTED TO BE AROUND 7.65 BILLION BAHT‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
